    byte from which an instruction may be loaded. \\
{\tt ITYPE} & The type of an instruction to be executed: $0$ for a number, and $1$ for an action. \\
{\tt I} & The {\tt I}nstruction. Holds the opcode of an instruction
    to be executed. \\
