{\tt RDEPTH} & The {\tt R}eturn stack {\tt DEPTH} (number of items on the return stack. \\
{\tt SSIZE} & The number of words allocated for the data stack. \\
{\tt RSIZE} & The number of words allocated for the return stack. \\
{\tt HANDLER} & The address {\tt PC} is set to when an exception is raised. \\
